                    <span class="opener__topics ">
            <a class="opener__topics-link " href="https://www.propublica.org/topics/immigration">Immigration</a>
        </span>
    
    <h1 class="opener__hed " >        When a Florida Farmer-Legislator Turned Against Immigration, the Consequences Were Severe. But Not for Him.
    </h1>

    <h2 class="opener__dek "  >        For a lawmaker’s political career and his farm, a federal visa program was a lifeline. For a young father trying to meet his son’s mounting medical needs, that same lifeline failed him.
    </h2>
    </div> <!-- Close .opener__topic-title-dek-wrapper -->

</div>
        
<div class="article-meta-1
     article-meta-1--left     " data-pp-location="article meta">

