                </div>

    
<figcaption class="attribution">
        <span class="attribution__caption">First image: The main road that runs through the small community of Cerritos in Guanajuato, Mexico, is lined with sunflower fields. Second image: Residents of Cerritos installed a blue gate following the kidnapping of a young woman.</span>
    
