    <h4>
        New here?
    </h4>
    <div class="bb-intro-module__dek">
        <p>We’re <a href="https://www.propublica.org/about">ProPublica</a>, a nonprofit, independent newsroom with one job: to hold the powerful to account. Here’s how we’re reporting on <a href="https://www.propublica.org/topics/democracy">democracy</a> this election season:</p>

    </div>
