    <div class="story-card__description">
                        <a class="story-card__series" href="https://www.propublica.org/series/the-new-immigration">The New Immigration</a>
        
        <h3 class="story-card__hed" >
            <a href="https://www.propublica.org/article/business-lobby-immigration-reform-trump">
                                    The U.S. Business Community Used to Be a Force for Immigration Reform. What Happened?
                            </a>
        </h3>

        <p class="story-card__dek" >
                            For decades, the business lobby fundamentally moderated the nation’s immigration debate. But in the age of Trump, fearful of advocating publicly on this issue, they’ve largely prioritized other things like corporate tax cuts and deregulation.
                    </p>

        <p class="story-card__byline">
            by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/eli-hager">Eli Hager</a>,             <time class="timestamp" datetime="2024-10-25EDT05:00">Oct. 25, 5 a.m. EDT</time>
        </p>

            </div>
